quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  25,44,"Noma ucabanga ukuthi iningi labo liyezwa noma linomqondo yini na? Abayilutho ngaphandle kokufana nezinkomo, Qhabo bona baphambuke endleleni ngokwedlulele"
  25,45,"Awuboni yini ukuthi iNkosi yakho iwelula kanjani umthunzi, ukube yayithanda yayizowenza ukuthi umendawonye sabe sesenza ilanga ukuthi libe yisibonakaliso kuwona"
  25,46,Bese siwuletha kuthina siwuletha kancane kancane
  25,47,Futhi nguyena (uMvelinqangi) owanenzela ubusuku babayisembozo kanye nokulala kwaba ukuphumula futhi wenza imini kwaba ngeyokuvuka (kusetshenzwe)
  25,48,Futhi nguyena othumela imimoya njengezindaba ezinhle ngaphambi komusa wakhe futhi sawehlisela phansi amanzi (imvula) emsulwa ephuma esibhakabhakeni
  25,49,Ukuze siphilise ngawo izwe elifile futhi siwaphuzise lokho esakudalayo izinkomo kanye nabantu abaningi
  25,50,Futhi ngempela sayisabalalisa phakathi kwabo ukuze bakhumbule kepha iningi labantu alivumi lutho ngaphandle kwabangakholwayo
  25,51,Futhi ukube sasithanda sasizoveza umexwayisi kuwona wonke amadolobha
  25,52,Ngakho-ke ningabahloniphi (ningabalaleli) abangakholwa futhi zabalaza ubhekane nabo ngayo (iQurâ€™an) ukuzabalaza kanzima
  25,53,"Futhi nguyena owadedela izinhlobo ezimbili zolwandle lolu oluhlwabusile olumtoti kanye nalolu olusasawoti olubabayo futhi wabeka isehlukaniso phakathi kwazo zombili, isehlukaniso ekungavumelekile ukuba seqiwe"
  25,54,Futhi nguyena owadala umuntu ngamanzi futhi wamenzela izinhlobonhlobo zegazi nomshado futhi ngasosonke isikhathi iNkosi yakho inamandla okwenza zonke izinto
  25,55,Futhi esikhundleni sikaMvelinqangi bakhonza lokho okungeke kubasize nokungeke kubalimaze futhi ngasosonke isikhathi ongakholwayo ungumsizi ekulweni neNkosi yakhe